{"tid":416981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾企街不得好死","createTime":"2017-09-28T08:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T06:18:38.000Z","uid":390,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"867447a0079243e2168596e1f50b47f1db03978e","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"唔係講緊深水埗/廟街嗰啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係講緊嗰啲乜撚野<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">籌募大使</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說啱啱收工行緊返屋企，經過成堆藍色衫拎住塊板嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經開始迴避佢哋，費時佢哋嘥口水，我又要諗藉口拒絕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我一路同個客傾電話一路喺佢哋側邊經過<br />\n屌奶星有條女喪屍咁箭步衝埋嚟大嗌：「先生！先生！聯合國兒童基金會搵你幫幫手呀！」<br />\n我都已經講咗句：「唔需要，唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n佢仲要繼續跟住我：「點解呀？唔好傾電話住啦先生！好快㗎咋！」<br />\n屌你老尾我同個客傾緊重要嘢 班撚屌仲要繼續嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌左佢一聲 個客依家以為我鬧鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祝籌募大使不得好死</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac7ca168ac2508e0dfdef110863be3d609deda0","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cd1954efe153155270ea681fc2ea6cde4a2a49","tid":416981,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"870ae1650c362de090d84bac94c2ad851bc3afb5","tid":416981,"uid":40272,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:55:13.000Z","msg":"之前睇港台31金錢國度<br />\n呢啲唔係慈善機構員工<br />\n呢啲企街係慈善機構外判比出面公司專門<br />\n負責兜客 ，兜到個上限有錢分<br />\n企街呢班人出發點係為自己"},{"pid":"5cc92564e121333ea365781d25e7f680a6b5713f","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T08:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前睇港台31金錢國度<br />\n呢啲唔係慈善機構員工<br />\n呢啲企街係慈善機構外判比出面公司專門<br />\n負責兜客 ，兜到個上限有錢分<br />\n企街呢班人出發點係為自己</blockquote><br />\n依家仲要冇撚得投訴 因為根本冇牌照規管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b4367d73ea0cbd24d60dfbde018aae07190a5e","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始叫人簽名<br />\n再說鳩你長期捐錢<br />\n同保險狗一樣咁低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2628288a613f2510348bc74e092edebe96e78e3c","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79be5a27e4bd526b7e252d48997993580787d2e","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11d7cea7f1e7d14d68bc19fe8ac2a11e4f094e7","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T09:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse