":"2017-09-28T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會直接當佢地透明，眼尾望都唔望佢地一眼，望住正前面掂行掂過<br />\n<br />\n巴打下次可以試吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經當佢透明掂行掂過 <br />\n冇諗過佢會過份到突登大大聲叫我唔好傾電話<br />\n屌佢老母臭西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7a01e1020dd711c0ada897cb81affc8c9b0d1c","tid":416981,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"又真係好多on9每個月比錢佢地洗 <br />\n結果比佢地掠曬水養到佢地咁多人 個個出糧比佢地企"},{"pid":"9e95fbeea7e7376fa9bc7cc3eaad7a19162affbc","tid":416981,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又真係好多on9每個月比錢佢地洗 <br />\n結果比佢地掠曬水養到佢地咁多人 個個出糧比佢地企</blockquote><br />\n唉屌屋企人都試過有份養呢班蛀米蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好在一早cut撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657b9ee8579ae15eb3eb0836f704f51211de9fec","tid":416981,"uid":33936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"同佢地四目交投果下已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}